<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/"><channel><title>Dust Extraction Systems on eQualle Blog</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/categories/dust-extraction-systems/</link><description>Recent posts on eQualle Blog</description><generator>Hugo 0.150.1</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://blog.equalle.com/categories/dust-extraction-systems/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Wet Sanding Options To Minimize Airborne Dust</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 23 Jan 2026 13:49:31 +0000</pubDate><category>Dust Extraction Systems</category><category>grit-60</category><category>grit-320</category><category>grit-400</category><category>grit-600</category><category>grit-3000</category><category>wet sanding</category><category>dry sanding</category><category>joint compound</category><description>Engineer-tested wet sanding methods that cut airborne dust, improve finish quality, and speed cleanup. Tools, media, safety, and practical tips inside.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="wet-methods-for-dustless-sanding-indoors"&gt;Wet Methods for Dustless Sanding Indoors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On a quiet Saturday, I watched sunbeams pick up a blizzard of drywall dust in a small, lived‑in apartment. The hallway was taped for paint, a crib sat two doors down, and a stack of sandpaper waited on the drop cloth. Every swipe of a sanding pole cast more white into the air. The homeowner—mask on, windows open—was doing their best, but dust still found a way into the return vents and the closets. I’ve worked in labs and on job sites long enough to know that dust damage isn’t just aesthetic; it creeps into electronics, triggers allergies, and lingers in HVAC systems for months. The question that matters to families and contractors alike becomes practical, not theoretical: can we keep the surface quality high while keeping the air clean?&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/20.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/pinterest/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/pinterest/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/pinterest/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/23/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/wet-sanding-options-to-minimize-airborne-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>12</readingTime></item><item><title>Negative Pressure Setup To Control Dust Spread</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 02 Jan 2026 13:38:37 +0000</pubDate><category>Dust Extraction Systems</category><category>grit-180</category><category>dust control</category><description>Design negative-pressure containment and pair it with dustless sanding to stop jobsite dust at the source. Specs, airflow math, tools, and pro tips.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="dustless-sanding-and-negative-pressure-mastery"&gt;Dustless Sanding and Negative Pressure Mastery&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can almost hear the sigh when the first pass of 120-grit levels a joint, the wall turning from patched to pristine. Then the moment breaks—fine powder blooms into the light, spiraling toward the hallway where a toddler naps and the HVAC returns hum. Anyone who has lived through a remodel knows that dust isn’t just a nuisance; it migrates through door gaps, rides thermal currents, and infiltrates electronics, textiles, and lungs. That’s why modern workflows pair dustless sanding at the tool with a properly engineered negative-pressure setup for the room. One contains the debris at its source; the other controls the air itself, ensuring any fugitive particles move in only one direction—out.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/04.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/cards/pinterest/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/cards/pinterest/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/cards/pinterest/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/02/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/negative-pressure-setup-to-control-dust-spread-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>11</readingTime></item><item><title>Use Bag Plus Hepa Filter For Drywall Dust</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 13 Dec 2025 13:32:51 +0000</pubDate><category>Dust Extraction Systems</category><category>grit-100</category><category>grit-150</category><category>grit-320</category><description>Learn how to pair a HEPA bag and filter for dustless sanding, keeping drywall dust under control with cleaner air, faster cleanup, and pro-grade results.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="dustless-sanding-with-hepa-bags-for-drywall-dust"&gt;Dustless sanding with HEPA bags for drywall dust&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first time you sand fresh drywall, you learn how sneaky the dust can be. It drifts like fog—settling in coffee cups, clinging to jackets by the door, finding its way into rooms you never even entered. A weekend project becomes a week of wiping, vacuuming, and still catching a powdery haze in the afternoon sun. If you’re living in the space you’re renovating, the frustration is double: family life doesn’t pause while you sand. That’s why the right setup—pairing a vacuum bag with a true HEPA filter and a sander built for dustless sanding—changes everything. It’s not just cleaner; it’s calmer. You notice the shift the first time you turn off the sander and the air looks the same as it did before you started.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/17.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/pinterest/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/pinterest/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/pinterest/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/13/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/use-bag-plus-hepa-filter-for-drywall-dust-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>11</readingTime></item><item><title>Seal Fittings To Prevent Vacuum Leaks</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 28 Nov 2025 13:35:39 +0000</pubDate><category>Dust Extraction Systems</category><category>grit-60</category><category>dry sanding</category><description>Learn how to seal fittings to prevent vacuum leaks for cleaner, safer dustless sanding. Practical seal types, testing steps, and maintenance tips.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="seal-fittings-to-stop-vacuum-leaks-for-dustless-sanding"&gt;Seal Fittings to Stop Vacuum Leaks for Dustless Sanding&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You notice the air first. It’s still. The living room is taped off, the baseboards are off, and your heart is set on getting through the weekend project without a whiteout of debris coating every surface you own. Your plan is simple: refinish the floors with dustless sanding so you can skip the week-long cleanup and the endless sneezing. The shop vac hums, your sander spins up, and for a few minutes it feels like a win. Then the hose trembles. A faint hiss rises near a quick-connect. You see it—the telltale plume of fines floating off the pad. You lift your mask a touch, eyes scanning the fittings. The promise of an almost dust-free job hinges on the invisible: airtight connections.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/03.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/cards/pinterest/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/cards/pinterest/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/cards/pinterest/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/28/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/seal-fittings-to-prevent-vacuum-leaks-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>12</readingTime></item><item><title>Multi Hole Discs Improve Airflow And Cut</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 15 Nov 2025 14:04:48 +0000</pubDate><category>Dust Extraction Systems</category><category>grit-80</category><category>grit-100</category><category>grit-180</category><category>joint compound</category><category>orbital sander</category><description>Learn how multi-hole discs boost airflow, cut rate, and surface finish while keeping dustless sanding clean and precise in wood, auto, and drywall jobs.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="dustless-sanding-multi-hole-discs-that-cut-faster"&gt;Dustless sanding: multi-hole discs that cut faster&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On a Saturday morning in the shop, the light comes in as a hazy beam. You flip on the sander, nudge it onto an oak tabletop, and within seconds the air looks like a snow globe gone rogue. Your safety glasses fog, your shirt turns gray, and the shop vac whines like it’s doing something—but the dust still settles on every flat surface you own. I’ve been there. I’ve also watched the other version of this scene: the pad spins, dust disappears, the workpiece stays cool, and the abrasive keeps biting for pass after pass. The difference isn’t magic—it&amp;rsquo;s airflow. Specifically, the way a multi-hole disc and a properly set vacuum system handle air and debris to deliver real dustless sanding without killing your cut rate.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/16.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/multi-hole-discs-improve-airflow-and-cut-dustless-sandi