ner results.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="dustless-sanding-setup-with-hepa-dust-extractors"&gt;Dustless Sanding Setup with HEPA Dust Extractors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On a quiet Saturday morning, you roll your sanding cart to the center of the room. The cabinets are masked, the floor is taped, and the sander’s pad lies face-up like a promise. The house is occupied—kids already drawing at the kitchen table—so emitting a fine fog of particulate is not an option. This is where dustless sanding becomes more than a phrase; it’s a standard of care. Switch on the extractor; it hums to life with a steady pitch, a different sound than a shop vac—lower, tighter, purposeful. The sander’s brush skirt seals to the workpiece, and the paper’s multi-hole pattern lines up with the pad like a gasket. Your first pass is a whisper of rotation and consistent cut. No haze in the light shafts, no grit on your tongue, no need to pause when someone walks by. The job feels clean in a way that’s as much about process control as it is about comfort.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/set-up-hepa-dust-extractors-for-sanding-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/set-up-hepa-dust-extractors-for-sanding-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/set-up-hepa-dust-extractors-for-sanding-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/set-up-hepa-dust-extractors-for-sanding-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/set-up-hepa-dust-extractors-for-sanding-dustless-sanding/cards/facebook/set-up-hepa-dust-extractors-for-sanding-dustless-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/set-up-hepa-dust-extractors-for-sanding-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/set-up-hepa-dust-extractors-for-sanding-dustless-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/set-up-hepa-dust-extractors-for-sanding-dustless-sanding/cards/instagram/set-up-hepa-dust-extractors-for-sanding-dustless-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/set-up-h